e":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"未撚玩過高refresh rate monitor就咪撚出聲話冇分別啦<br />\n<br />\n其實啲人話24fps以上分唔到係講緊影片，因為條片每格入面包含咗額外資料，例如motion blur，令人眼睇落已經好順<br />\n<br />\n但遊戲畫面係由gpu逐格渲染出嚟，每一格只包含果格應有嘅嘢，所以要高fps先令人覺得順，而呢個就係點解vr headset(htc vive, oculus rift cv1)要將個refresh rate去到90hz，因為至少90hz refresh rate先會令人眼覺得順到同現實一樣，減少motion sickness"},{"pid":"7e679809f2afd83bf22902105540ca8876fcbbc4","tid":546483,"uid":138188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:55:26.000Z","msg":"你同一隻GAME玩過60以上同得2-30你就明個分別係邊<br />\n<br />\n由其係動作GAME FPS低真係想死<br />\n<br />\n咁當然有人PICK GAME睇畫面唔睇遊戲性又另一回事"},{"pid":"f0ba4871ad60059a66e85e9257bdcb824ebde59b","tid":546483,"uid":13545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T03:02:34.000Z","msg":"The last of us remaster<br />\n玩過60fps之後轉30fps就會知個分別<br />\n60fps明顯smooth好多"},{"pid":"487cbcca6c7b2cec6fb6884f8ad7ef48ca407d17","tid":546483,"uid":71519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"50-144fps基本上無分別?<br />\n<br />\n你對唔對得住生對眼比你既老豆老母?"},{"pid":"9116c0bb0adfb21aa403286046c24d9c85abfd4a","tid":546483,"uid":76527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"同意你個標題，但你內文太9唔搭8.<br />\n<br />\n60同144個分別正常人都睇到分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6243cd0970c0de74bb7320fc925686615e5f82e3","tid":546483,"uid":5348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"樓主只係未試過高fps <br />\n淨係youtube睇人個d fps 測試就覺得自己試過高fps同低fps既分別姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e199cf1d4b71819e25ff66f4a4f2f16df0cc30fe","tid":546483,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f100d5906ae9ae1bf0aa37f61807b50acf7ded06","tid":546483,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ee74a206cdd1c5bb35c459d8af681